      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "Manners let RICK REILLY NZ (5) down when he was in the market at Menangle last start but he had been producing some solid efforts prior including a third in a higher-graded race the only time he raced here. He is up to winning this with his A-game. MR TEDDY NZ (10) looks close to a win having come from a wide barrier for second at his latest appearance at Menangle, beaten 2.2 metres. With a little luck from the back row he could go one better. OBADIAH DRAGON NZ (3) is another with the hoof on the till after two successive placings at Newcastle, both from wider barriers than this. CONSTANTINA (2) drew on the back row last start but led to win prior so is much better served by this barrier.",
